timeline.bodyText:
I think this might be too narrow at this level of the DSL. Given #7395, I wonder if a better setup would be:
http
    .passwordManagement(pass -> pass
        .changePasswordPage("/my-page")
    );
This seems like a good fit for other password management components down the road:
http
    .passwordManagement(pass -> pass
        .changePasswordPage("/my-page")
        .changePasswordProcessingUrl("/my-processing-url")
        .passwordChecker(...)
        .passwordEncoder(...)
        // ...
    );
I like changePasswordPage since that aligns with loginPage

